	<div class="attorna-single-article clearfix" >
		<div class="attorna-single-article-content"><div class="pf-content"><p>Although it ruled that Indiana’s ban on same-sex marriage was unconstitutional, the 7th Circuit has now granted Attorney General Zoeller’s request for a stay on that ruling until the U.S. Supreme Court acts on Indiana’s appeal requesting that the ruling be overturned.</p>
<p>For more information, please contact Indiana attorney <a title="Attorney Profile: Steve Lavallo" href="https://kddk.com/attorneys/stephen-s-lavallo/">Steve Lavallo</a> at (812) 423-3183 or <a href="mailto:SLavallo@KDDK.com">slavallo@KDDK.com</a>.</p>
<h3>About the Author</h3>
<figure id="attachment_10048" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-10048" style="width: 195px" class="wp-caption alignleft"><a href="https://kddk.com/lavallo_steve-kddk-2015-3x4-195x260/"><img class="wp-image-10048 size-full" title="SteveLavalloWeb4_3" src="https://kddk.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Lavallo_Steve-KDDK-2015-3x4-195x260.jpg" alt="" width="195" height="260" /></a><figcaption id="caption-attachment-10048" class="wp-caption-text">Steve Lavallo</figcaption></figure>
<p><a title="Attorney Profile: Steve Lavallo" href="https://kddk.com/attorneys/stephen-s-lavallo/"><em>Stephen S. Lavallo</em></a><em>, a partner at the law firm Kahn, Dees, Donovan &amp; Kahn, LLP, in Evansville, Indiana, has more than 25 years’ experience in the practice of <a title="Practice Area: Estate Planning &amp; Probate Administration" href="https://kddk.com/practice-areas/estate-planning/"><em>estate planning and administration law</em></a>, <a title="Practice Area: Workers Compensation Defense" href="https://kddk.com/practice-areas/workers-compensation-defense/">worker’s compensation defense</a></em><em>, <a title="Practice Area: Business Law" href="https://kddk.com/practice-areas/business-law/">business law</a></em><em>, and <a title="Practice Area: Real Estate Law" href="https://kddk.com/practice-areas/real-estate-law/">real estate law</a></em><em>, and is a certified civil <a title="Practice Area: Mediation" href="https://kddk.com/practice-areas/mediation/">mediator</a>. He represents businesses, both large and small, as well as individuals in a wide variety of business transactions, organization, sales and leasing of properties, and in the defense of companies from worker’s compensation claims. In addition, Steve advises individuals in connection with their estate and wealth transfer planning and during the process of probate and trust administration.</em></p>
